---
title: Spicy Shrimp & Broccoli Stir-Fry in a Sweet Chili Soy Glaze over Jasmine Rice
description: Love shrimp and broccoli? Then you’ll adore our tasty twist on the tried-and-true classic. Succulent seared shrimp and tender broccoli are simmered in a sweet chili and soy sauce mixture that’s spiked with fresh ginger. On the side, there’s a heap of steamy jasmine rice (aka the perfect vessel for catching any delicious runaway sauce). Skip the takeout joint and find out how easy and tasty it is to whip up this dish in your very own kitchen... in just 20 minutes, no less!
